00:23:23,570 --> 00:23:25,822
Exactly! Exactly!

528
00:23:26,073 --> 00:23:27,115
Ah, there you are, Sybil.

529
00:23:27,366 --> 00:23:28,492
Good evening, Major.

530
00:23:28,742 --> 00:23:30,577
Evening,
Mrs. Fawlty.

531
00:23:30,828 --> 00:23:32,830
- There you are, your Lordship.
