00:23:40,379 --> 00:23:42,089
Used to be quite
a hobby of mine.

537
00:23:42,339 --> 00:23:43,298
Little investment too.

538
00:23:43,549 --> 00:23:45,175
Quite.
Talking about, um,

539
00:23:45,425 --> 00:23:49,096
- Did you manage to...
- Oh yes.

540
00:23:49,638 --> 00:23:53,141
- There you are, your Lordship.
- Oh, Thank you, yes.

541
00:24:01,650 --> 00:24:02,943
Yes, you know,
these sorts of things,

542
00:24:03,193 --> 00:24:06,196
their value's soared this
last couple of years.

