547
00:24:11,535 --> 00:24:13,996
Yes, yes, I will.

548
00:24:14,246 --> 00:24:16,123
You can't take any risks
nowadays, I'm afraid.

549
00:24:16,373 --> 00:24:17,541
- No, no, quite.
- Well, I must be off.

550
00:24:17,791 --> 00:24:18,959
Thank you very much,
your Lordship.

551
00:24:19,209 --> 00:24:20,419
Basil!

552
00:24:20,669 --> 00:24:22,045
