a quick look at them,

565
00:24:48,655 --> 00:24:50,073
and find their
current value.

566
00:24:50,324 --> 00:24:52,493
- Would you really?
- Yes, yes, certainly.

567
00:24:52,743 --> 00:24:54,328
Well, I'll be off
in a few moments.

568
00:24:54,578 --> 00:24:55,537
