- Basil!

569
00:24:55,787 --> 00:24:58,207
I'm talking to Lord Melbury!

570
00:24:58,457 --> 00:25:02,878
A gin and orange, a lemon squash
and a scotch and water, please!

571
00:25:03,128 --> 00:25:06,256
All right!
All right!

572
00:25:09,551 --> 00:25:10,385
Oh, Mr. Fawlty...

573
00:25:10,636 --> 00:25:11,637
