00:27:46,250 --> 00:27:48,544
Would you mind filling
this out, please?

634
00:27:48,794 --> 00:27:51,129
We've given you room...
aha!

635
00:27:51,380 --> 00:27:52,339
Ah, Fawlty!

636
00:27:52,589 --> 00:27:55,467
Mr. Fawlty to you,
Lord Melbury.

637
00:27:55,717 --> 00:27:56,552
I beg your pardon?

638
00:27:56,802 --> 00:27:58,428
Oh, nothing,
please forget all about it.

639
00:27:58,679 --> 00:28:01,557
Here's the check
for £-200.

640
00:28:01,807 --> 00:28:04,476
Ah, thank you
so much.

