00:28:12,067 --> 00:28:12,860
- Ah, yes.
- No, I don't.

646
00:28:13,110 --> 00:28:13,986
Because we've
just heard

647
00:28:14,236 --> 00:28:15,946
that the duke
of Buckleigh is dead!

648
00:28:16,196 --> 00:28:18,699
Yes, got his head knocked off
by a golf ball.

649
00:28:18,949 --> 00:28:20,492
Tragic! Tragic!

650
00:28:20,742 --> 00:28:22,744
Well, how are you,
Lord Melbury?

651
00:28:22,995 --> 00:28:25,706
'ow are yer then?
All right, mate?

652
00:28:25,956 --> 00:28:29,585
'ow's me
old mucker?

653
00:28:29,793 --> 00:28:31,003
Any valuables to deposit,
Sir Richard?

654
00:28:31,253 --> 00:28:33,839
Any bricks?

655
00:28:34,298 --> 00:28:38,218
I do apologize...
You bastard!

656
00:28:38,468 --> 00:28:39,761
We've given
you room 12

