00:30:34,084 --> 00:30:35,002
Sorry about that,
Mr. Fawlty.

680
00:30:35,252 --> 00:30:36,336
Can I buy you
a drink?

681
00:30:36,587 --> 00:30:38,422
No, no, I'd better put
this up, I suppose.

682
00:30:38,672 --> 00:30:41,258
Basil!

683
00:30:41,341 --> 00:30:44,303
A gin and orange,

